          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Innovation in Accreditation Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow the Department of Education to waive accreditation requirements if an accrediting agency or association demonstrates that a waiver is necessary to enable an institution of higher education or an accredited program to implement innovative practices. </p>]]></text>
